      ],
      "text": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\">A genetics educator is presenting a lecture on mitochondrial DNA (mtDNA) to provide students with a comprehensive understanding of its characteristics and inheritance patterns. The educator provides several statements about mtDNA and asks the students to identify which one is inaccurate. Which of the following statements about mitochondrial DNA is false?</span></p>",
      "unique_key": "Q9294049",
